[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Technical Issue Encountered**                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m All POST requests to `/admin.php` resulted in PHP errors:                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Notice: Undefined index: username in /var/www/html/admin.php on line 17      [32m│[0m
