[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m This indicates that **PHP is not receiving the POST body data** from the     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m requests. The issue appears to be with how the `pw_send_payload` tool (using [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Playwright) is transmitting POST body data to the server.                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
